18
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:19,840
We can't both shower at the same time, Lea.

19
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:22,630
One of us would block the steam of water for the other.

20
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:25,140
Oh, Shaun, this is not for the purpose of cleanliness.

21
00:00:25,140 --> 00:00:27,850
This is for the purpose of having sex with you.

22
00:00:31,390 --> 00:00:32,850
N-no. No.

23
00:00:32,850 --> 00:00:35,440
It would be inconvenient, possibly dangerous.

24
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:37,690
Soap might get into difficult places.

25
00:00:37,690 --> 00:00:39,360
If we leaned against the shower handle,

26
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:40,360
